                     <interp inst="t18220417-94-person931" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . This is the coal-bag I lent Gilson.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-94-person932">
                  WILLIAM 
                  CREE
               <interp inst="t18220417-94-person932" type="surname" value="CREE"></interp>
