                     <interp inst="t18220417-94-person932" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am pawnbroker, and live in Gray's Inn-lane. On the 19th of February a petticoat was pawned for 9 d. The duplicate found on Marsh is what I gave the person.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-94-person933">
                  ROBERT 
                  KENDREW
               <interp inst="t18220417-94-person933" type="surname" value="KENDREW"></interp>
