               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>MARSH - <rs id="t18220417-94-verdict479" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220417-94-verdict479" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
